<tr>
<td width="600" colspan="4">
<b>Description</b><br>
This shield is dropped by the Giant Heart Spider who can be found near the zone to Innothule Swamp.  He is a rare spawn, and you must keep killing all the spiders that spawn in the room to make him pop.  The shield is the common drop with the Chitin Shell Armor being the rare loot.</td>
